title: We Can't Believe How Much Our Intern Made From Selling Feet Pictures
description:
Our intern Bella used to sell feet pics for money. The account she sold to started following her in high school. But at the time, she was hesitant about taking them up on their offer. But in college, she decided to give it a try, and she made hundreds!
